Aheza Kiros (amụrụ na 16 Ọktoba na afọ 1985 na Tigray) bụ onye Ethiopia na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge nke maara nke ọma na mita 10,000.
Ọ mechara nke anọ na 2006 African Championships na nke iri na asaa na 2007 World Championships

N'ịgba ọsọ na 2009 Adidas Track Classic, ọ meriri Ejegayehu Dibaba na mita 5000 na ọrụ mbụ ya n'okpuru nkeji iri na ise nke 14:56.33. O meriri n'ọsọ Carlsbad 5000 n'afọ ahụ, mana ọ bụ onye na-esote n'afọ sochirinụ iji nweta ihe ndekọ Meseret Defar. Ọ bụ onye nke atọ na 2010 Great Ethiopian Run na obodo Addis Ababa, na-emecha usoro ahụ na nkeji 33:59.
N'ọnwa Machị na-esote, o mere nke mbụ ya n'ime ọkara marathon wee bụrụ nke atọ n'ime oge 1:09:10 na Paris Half Marathon

O nwere mmeri nke abụọ nke ọrụ ya na Carlsbad 5000 n'ọnwa Eprel afọ 2011, ọ bụkwa onye nke abụọ na Freihofer's Run for Women na June ahụ. Ọ bụkwa onye nke abụọ na New York Mini 10K, na-aga n'ihu onye Ethiopia ibe ya Belaynesh Zemedkun. N'ọnwa Ọgọstụ, ọ ghọrọ nwanyị Ethiopia mbụ meriri na Beach to Beacon 10K. O mere marathon mbụ ya na Dubai Marathon wee bịa nke iri na ise n'ime awa 2:33:21

Ọ bụ onye nke abụọ na New York Mini 10K maka afọ nke abụọ na-agba ọsọ na June. Ọ bụkwa onye nke abụọ na ihe omume abụọ nke Boston Athletic, na-agba ọsọ nke 31:57 nkeji na BAA 10K ma na-ewere nke abụọ na Boston Half Marathon.
Aheza mere marathon mbụ ya na asọmupi 2013 Dubai Marathon ebe nke anọ na ọsọ ya nke 2:24:30 awa.
